>From: "Steve Bradley" <scscomp(-at-)bellsouth.net>
>Date: Sat, 30 Mar 2002 12:45:45 -0500
>
>I've got a replacement speedo in my crewcab. How do I tell if it is
>calibrated for 14 inch or 15inch wheels? 

Look for a "W" stamped on the back, followed by a number.  Per the
Bentley manual, page E-14 1, the numbers should be as follows:

      14"    15"
kph  0.496  0.48
mph  0.8    0.77

Matt Roberds


